---
// How It Works section explaining the four-skill pipeline
---

<section class="how-it-works" data-test="how-it-works" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="methodology-section" data-test="methodology-section">
      <h2>How RootSpec Works</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">
        RootSpec provides a four-command pipeline that transforms product ideas
        into tested, working software through structured specification.
      </p>

      <div class="pipeline-steps">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3><code>/rs-init</code></h3>
            <p>Initialize project structure with RootSpec framework files and validation prerequisites.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3><code>/rs-spec</code></h3>
            <p>Create validated specification through interview-driven process with built-in quality checks.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3><code>/rs-impl</code></h3>
            <p>Generate working code from specification using test-driven implementation with autonomous development.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">4</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3><code>/rs-validate</code></h3>
            <p>Run comprehensive tests against specification to verify implementation meets requirements.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="before-after-section" data-test="before-after-section">
        <h3>Before vs After RootSpec</h3>
        <div class="comparison-grid">
          <div class="before-content" data-test="before-content">
            <h4>Before: Traditional Approach</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Vague requirements</li>
              <li>Scope drift</li>
              <li>Implementation gaps</li>
              <li>Manual testing</li>
              <li>Inconsistent AI output</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="after-content" data-test="after-content">
            <h4>After: RootSpec Methodology</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Structured hierarchy</li>
              <li>Clear constraints</li>
              <li>Testable acceptance criteria</li>
              <li>Automated validation</li>
              <li>Reliable AI integration</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .how-it-works {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background-color: var(--bg-light);
  }

  .methodology-section h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
  }

  .section-intro {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .pipeline-steps {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .step-number {
    background-color: var(--primary-blue);
    color: white;
    width: 3rem;
    height: 3rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .step-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
  }

  .step-content code {
    background-color: var(--bg-gray);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
  }

  .step-content p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .before-after-section h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
  }

  .comparison-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .before-content, .after-content {
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--border-gray);
  }

  .before-content {
    background-color: #fef2f2;
    border-color: #fecaca;
  }

  .after-content {
    background-color: #f0fdf4;
    border-color: #bbf7d0;
  }

  .before-content h4 {
    color: #b91c1c;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .after-content h4 {
    color: #166534;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .comparison-grid ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .comparison-grid li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .before-content li::before {
    content: "✗";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #b91c1c;
  }

  .after-content li::before {
    content: "✓";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #166534;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .how-it-works {
      padding: 3rem 0;
    }

    .methodology-section h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .comparison-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .step {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>